-- Vodafone Greek Unit’s Employees Plan Work Stoppage, ANA Reports
-- B y   T o m   S t o u k a s
-- 2012-06-11T11:40:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-11/vodafone-greek-unit-s-employees-plan-work-stoppage-ana-reports.html
Employees at  Vodafone Group Plc (VOD) ’s
Greek subsidiary are planning a work stoppage tomorrow in
response to a management proposal to cut wages and benefits by
20 percent, Athens News Agency reported, without citing anyone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
